title: Jung Joon Young releases 'Me And You' MV featuring Jang Hye Jin | allkpop.com
text:
Or Login / Register With Us Forgot Password? Remember Me Jung Joon Young releases 'Me And You' MV featuring Jang Hye Jin By KpopJoA 6 minutes ago 537 51 0 0 Singer Jung Joon Young has unveiled his new ballad "Me and You" featuring Jang Hye Jin .
The song illustrates one's longing for his past lover, as Jung Joon Young and Jang Hye Jin give a powerful duet in "Me and You." The MV features a sad love story that fits the mood of the song. 
Check out the MV above!
